author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Innofactor To Cooperate With Folkuniversitetet In Sweden
text:
Jan 24 (Reuters) - Innofactor Plc:
* REG-FOLKUNIVERSITETET SELECTS INNOFACTOR AS THE PARTNER FOR IMPLEMENTING COURSE AND EVENT MANAGEMENT SYSTEM
* ‍PROJECT DELIVERY ESTIMATION WILL BE DURING YEARS 2018 AND 2019.​
* ‍PRICE (EXCLUDING VAT) OF PROCUREMENT IS ABOUT EUR 0.5 MILLION.​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
